# Project Management & Deployment
> Authority: See authority.mdc

【PLAN】 **All deployments require comprehensive planning with `todo_write` tool first.**

## Deployment Workflow
1. **Review State** - `git status --porcelain` + examine all modified/untracked files 【VALIDATE】
2. **Stage & Commit** - Comprehensive commit message documenting all changes and achievements
3. **Deploy & Monitor** - Push to trigger CI/CD, verify deployment success 【STOP】
4. **Document** - Update progress tracking with deployment results and live URLs

## Example
```
todo_write: Review git → Stage changes → Commit with full context → Push → Monitor CI/CD → Update docs
```